<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
{{template "head.gohtml" .}}
<body>
{{template "nav_new.gohtml" .}}
<main>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content">
            <article class="article-detail">
                <h1 style="margin-bottom: 18px;">友情链接</h1>

                <!-- 社区类 -->
                <h2 class="links-group-title"><span class="group-icon group-icon-community"></span>社区类</h2>
                <div class="links-list">
                    <a class="friend-link-card community" href="https://segmentfault.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="/static/pic/default-avatar.png" alt="SegmentFault logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">SegmentFault 思否</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">中国领先的开发者技术社区</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="friend-link-card community" href="https://www.v2ex.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="https://www.v2ex.com/static/icon-192.png" alt="V2EX logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">V2EX</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">创意工作者的社区</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="friend-link-card community" href="https://www.oschina.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="/static/pic/default-avatar.png" alt="开源中国 logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">开源中国</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">中文开源技术交流社区</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="friend-link-card community" href="https://learnku.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="/static/pic/default-avatar.png" alt="Leanku logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">LearnKu</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">专为终身学习者定制的编程知识社区</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- 博客类 -->
                <h2 class="links-group-title"><span class="group-icon group-icon-blog"></span>博客类</h2>
                <div class="links-list">
                    <a class="friend-link-card blog" href="https://coolshell.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="/static/pic/default-avatar.png" alt="酷壳 logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">酷壳 - CoolShell</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">陈皓的技术博客</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="friend-link-card blog" href="https://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="/static/pic/default-avatar.png" alt="阮一峰 logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">阮一峰的网络日志</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">科技、编程、互联网</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- 工具/产品类 -->
                <h2 class="links-group-title"><span class="group-icon group-icon-tool"></span>工具/产品类</h2>
                <div class="links-list">
                    <a class="friend-link-card tool" href="https://www.jetbrains.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="https://resources.jetbrains.com/storage/products/company/brand/logos/jb_beam.png" alt="JetBrains logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">JetBrains</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">开发者工具与 IDE</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="friend-link-card tool" href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/modules/logos_page/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="GitHub logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">GitHub</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">全球最大开源代码托管平台</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="links-tips">
                    <p>欢迎优秀社区、博客、技术站点交换友链！请联系站长或在 <a href="/link-contact" target="_blank">联系我们</a> 页面留言。</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>友情链接须知</h3>
                <ul class="links-rules">
                    <li>内容健康、合法，技术/学习/社区类优先</li>
                    <li>请保持贵站可访问且有本站友链</li>
                    <li>本站保留审核与下架权利</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>推荐社区</h3>
                <ul class="recommended-posts">
                    <li><a href="https://segmentfault.com/" target="_blank">SegmentFault 思否</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.v2ex.com/" target="_blank">V2EX</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.oschina.net/" target="_blank">开源中国</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://juejin.cn/" target="_blank">稀土掘金</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</main>
{{template "footer.gohtml" .}}
<style>
.links-group-title {
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 32px 0 12px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
}
.group-icon {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
.group-icon-community {
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='blue' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Ccircle cx='12' cy='12' r='10' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='M8 15a4 4 0 1 1 8 0' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
}
.group-icon-blog {
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='orange' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect x='4' y='4' width='16' height='16' rx='3' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='M8 8h8M8 12h8M8 16h4' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
}
.group-icon-tool {
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='green' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect x='6' y='6' width='12' height='12' rx='2' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='M9 9h6v6H9z' stroke-width='2'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
}

.links-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.friend-link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    min-width: 0;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-color);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    height: 80px;
}
.friend-link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(25,118,210,0.08);
    background: #f5faff;
}
.friend-link-card.community {
    border-left: 5px solid #1976d2;
}
.friend-link-card.blog {
    border-left: 5px solid #ff9800;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff7e6 0%, var(--card-bg) 80%);
}
[data-theme="dark"] {
    .friend-link-card.blog {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.1) 0%, var(--card-bg) 80%);
    }
    .friend-link-card.tool {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.1) 0%, var(--card-bg) 80%);
    }
}

.friend-link-card.tool {
    border-left: 5px solid #43a047;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e8f5e9 0%, var(--card-bg) 80%);
}
.friend-link-logo {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-right: 14px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    flex-shrink: 0;
}
.friend-link-info {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
}
.friend-link-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.friend-link-desc {
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--text-color-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.links-tips {
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
}
.links-tips a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
}
.links-rules {
    padding-left: 18px;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
}
.links-rules li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .links-list {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
}
@media (max-width: 700px) {
    .links-list {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .friend-link-card {
        padding: 10px 10px;
        height: 64px;
    }
    .friend-link-logo {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .friend-link-title {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
    }
    .friend-link-desc {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
}
</style>
</body>
</html>
